alright enough is enough.  no more about this.  I'm tired so this is gonna be 
short and to the point.

Ellen: Shape up your posts.  There are rules and they need to be followed.

LN: Shut up or make a char.  (I'll be tactful some other time.)

Kyle, Ellen, anyone else:  Keep religion off of the boards.  That means any 
religion.  I'm happy for your religious fervor, but some people in this world 
are easily offended and it just provokes arguments.  You want to save 
someone's soul take it off the board.

EVERYONE: any more unnessecary OOC: messages will result in a week's 
moderated posting.  i.e. you may post but only what is allowed by a moderator.


--part1_b8.2d26b8f6.2aad64d5_boundary
